1. During the last 7 days, on how many days did you do vigorous physical activities like heavy lifting, digging, aerobics, or fast bicycling? (in days) 
2. How much time did you usually spend doing vigorous physical activities on one of those days? (in days)
3. During the last 7 days, on how many days did you do moderate physical activities like carrying light loads, bicycling at a regular pace, or doubles tennis? Do not include walking. (in days)
4. How much time did you usually spend doing moderate physical activities on one of those days? (in minutes)
5. During the last 7 days, on how many days did you walk for at least 10 minutes at a time?   (in days)
6. How much time did you usually spend walking on one of those days? (in minutes) 
7. During the last 7 days, how much time did you spend sitting on a weekday? (in minutes, eg 5h -> 300 minutes)
